{"tid":1681591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得屌黑警做黑社會好撚on9？班黑警係唔會驚架","createTime":"2019-10-29T13:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T11:59:57.000Z","uid":27451,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f515e7bdf0e8e3d5f86f7de6470f6813e0b1015e","tid":1681591,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:55:48.000Z","msg":"即係咁，好多街坊見示威者屌黑警做黑社會，都唔知做乜鳩？<br />\n<br />\n而你地每次屌黑警係黑社會佢地都無乜反應，但你一屌佢係黑警屌佢係過街老鼠，佢哋就好似癲撚左咁追人黎咬，即係佢地真係好憎人話佢係黑警同過街老鼠架。"},{"pid":"cfb41527b5c62d75bc6d64afb9a01137b1af0b91","tid":1681591,"uid":136893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:56:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反思行動及行動數量<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（極緊急！！！）等我教大家點再引發群眾熱情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680895</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"07391b4d50bcaf2926e0a910fcd2ee36d9f08a8b","tid":1681591,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:56:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXEs9qi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXEs9qi.jpg&h=02cd3311&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mtm3RDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtm3RDU.jpg&h=fd9c9c47&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0e809ff2dfa71c15be8fa8149c62b0a2f9e57363","tid":1681591,"uid":62755,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:57:26.000Z","msg":"覺，仲有721831個句<br />\n呢堆垃圾根本唔覺得自己有錯<br />\n嗌黎做咩<br />\n直接叫佢地去自殺仲好"},{"pid":"95fd20059b20ad0a9c31323a4cc8580897237ac9","tid":1681591,"uid":96708,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:57:28.000Z","msg":"叫 你老婆比人屌，